current.terms_conditions_content:
What is Lorem Ipsum?

Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.
Why do we use it?
It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using 'Content here, content here', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for 'lorem ipsum' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).

settings.contact_title: DROP US A LINE | Schreiben Sie uns
settings.contact_text_desc: Have a question or comment? Use the form below to send us a message or contact us by mail at:

settings.question_faqs: 1. Are there any shipping and delivery charges for the orders? -
settings.answer_faqs: Delivery is free of charge for all our customers, all across India. However, we do charge for international deliveries, depending on the location.

settings.question_faqs: 2. What are the payment options available?
settings.answer_faqs:
We accept payments in multiple ways.

Credit Card - All scheduled bank credit cards.

Debit Card - All scheduled bank debit cards.

Net Banking - Every bank which has a net banking facility.

UPI - All major UPI platforms.

Mobile Wallet - Airtel Money, PayZapp , Freecharge , Ola Money, Jio Money , Phone Pe ,Paytm, Amazon Pay.

settings.question_faqs: 3. Which credit cards are accepted for domestic and international payments?
settings.answer_faqs: We list each and every scheduled bank credit cards. Simply select your preferred option from the list in our payments page and you're good to go.

settings.question_faqs: 4. Which domestic debit cards are accepted?
settings.answer_faqs: All payments are accepted through scheduled bank debit cards.

settings.question_faqs: 5. Which are the accepted Domestic Banks for Payments through Net Banking?
settings.answer_faqs: All net banking payments are processed through scheduled banks with adequate facilities.

settings.question_faqs: 6. Is Cash on Delivery available?
settings.answer_faqs: Yes, we do have Cash on Delivery (COD) service available.

settings.question_faqs: 7. How can I cancel my order
settings.answer_faqs: All orders can be cancelled through our website. Before an invoice is generated for the product of course.

settings.question_faqs: 8. How can I return my order?
settings.answer_faqs: All our products can be returned as per the return policy on our website

settings.question_faqs: 9. What is the return policy?
settings.answer_faqs: If the product received is not up to the mark, you can return it for up to 15 days after purchasing.

settings.question_faqs: 10. What is the refund policy?
settings.answer_faqs: Returned products that are unused and of good quality will be refunded within 15 days of receipt to the billing address.

settings.question_faqs: 11. What is the exchange policy?
settings.answer_faqs: No exchanges as per our current policy.

settings.question_faqs: 12. Do I need to pay for the return of the shipment if I chose to return the order?
settings.answer_faqs: Get easy, hassle free pickups and returns for every purchase.

settings.question_faqs: 13. Are all products eligible for return?
settings.answer_faqs: All products with manufacturing defects are eligible for returns.

settings.question_faqs: 14. Do you have no questions asked return policy?
settings.answer_faqs: While we'd love to make the return experience hassle free, we do not have such a policy.

settings.question_faqs: 15. How will I receive my refund?
settings.answer_faqs: Through RTGS / Bank Transfer as per refund request

settings.question_faqs: 16. How can I contact you in case of any queries?
settings.answer_faqs: We'd love to hear from you! Contact our customer care centre at 18001022256.

settings.question_faqs: 17. What is the warranty and repair policy for the order?
settings.answer_faqs: Please refer the Service & Warranty section on the website.

settings.question_faqs: 18. How will my order be delivered?
settings.answer_faqs: The deliveries are made through reputed courier companies.

settings.question_faqs: 19. How can I know the status of my order?
settings.answer_faqs: Once the order is shipped you will receive a AWB number via email/SMS. You can track the order on the website using the AWB number.

settings.question_faqs: 20. Where do you deliver in India?
settings.answer_faqs: We deliver across the country to over 17000 Plus Pin codes. Since there is a constant addition of pin codes, the exact number might vary from time to time.

settings.question_faqs: 21. What is the delivery timeline of my order?
settings.answer_faqs:
The general Delivery Timelines is as below, Within the City - 2-3 Days
Within the Region - 3-4 Days
Metro Cities - 3-5 Days
Rest of India - 4-7 Days
Special Regions - 7-9 Days
